Package it.polimi.ingsw.utils.messages

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClientMessage
    This interface should be implemented by every object representing an action that the player can perform.
    DisconnectMessage
    This interface represents disconnection messages, which have to be promptly handled.
    ServerMessage
    This interface represents messages coming from the server.
